Clean-room implementations (no third-party code copied)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The rank/select bit vector (rank9), the wavelet matrix, and the 4-ary quad
wavelet matrix in src/index/fmindex/ are clean-room implementations written
from the published papers listed in DESIGN.md (Provenance). No code was copied
from GPL-licensed projects (e.g. sdsl-lite, sux, pasta); those were used only
as external references for benchmarking and correctness cross-checks.
